, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7c60/dce5/668291_large.png?m=1704417546", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7c60/dce5/668291_xlarge.png?m=1704417546", "created": 1703413859, "last_modified": 1704417546}, "last_reply_by": "shoudeliao", "last_touched": 1710396101, "title": "有 Mac、Win 双修的老哥吗 关于快捷键适应问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1023495", "created": 1710382351, "deleted": 0, "content": "想请问下，如果同时用两种系统，比如，工作 windows ，回家 mac ，两者的快捷键好适应吗？\r\n最基础的比如复制粘贴，win 是小拇指按 ctrl ，在 mac 下却要用大拇指按 cmd 。", "content_rendered": "<p>想请问下，如果同时用两种系统，比如，工作 windows ，回家 mac ，两者的快捷键好适应吗？\n最基础的比如复制粘贴，win 是小拇指按 ctrl ，在 mac 下却要用大拇指按 cmd 。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1710382351, "replies": 76, "id": 1023495}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 216319, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4121, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 382312, "username": "ggp1ot2", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ggp1ot2", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_mini.png?m=1698654772", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_normal.png?m=1698654772", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_large.png?m=1698654772", "created": 1549503424, "last_modified": 1698654772}, "last_reply_by": "yohane3016", "last_touched": 1710343643, "title": "自己开公司给自己发高工资，有风险吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1023232", "created": 1710310065, "deleted": 0, "content": "打算 gap 一段时间\r\n\r\n比如让家人注册一个公司，每个月给我发高工资（比如封顶缴纳社保、公积金），可行吗？\r\n\r\n这里的可行，指的是这么做有没有什么风险。\r\n\r\n不考虑什么还要交税等给国家交钱的产生金钱上的顾虑。\r\n\r\n我个人的理解是，比如一个月发个三五万的，个人交税就要一定数目，然后公司层面可能也要给国家交一些费用？\r\n\r\n先不要喷，只是一个想法，具体动机：\r\n\r\n- 在没工作的期间，社保公积金不断\r\n- 办理一些信用卡、签证等业务，高额的社保基数，有一定的正向作用", "content_rendered": "<p>打算 gap 一段时间</p>\n<p>比如让家人注册一个公司，每个月给我发高工资（比如封顶缴纳社保、公积金），可行吗？</p>\n<p>这里的可行，指的是这么做有没有什么风险。</p>\n<p>不考虑什么还要交税等给国家交钱的产生金钱上的顾虑。</p>\n<p>我个人的理解是，比如一个月发个三五万的，个人交税就要一定数目，然后公司层面可能也要给国家交一些费用？</p>\n<p>先不要喷，只是一个想法，具体动机：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在没工作的期间，社保公积金不断</li>\n<li>办理一些信用卡、签证等业务，高额的社保基数，有一定的正向作用</li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1710310065, "replies": 74, "id": 1023232}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_large.png?m=1650127623", "name": "shenzhen", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_normal.png?m=1650127623", "title": "深圳", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen", "topics": 3016, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shenzhen", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1650127623", "stars": 1933, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 21, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 504124, "username": "aw2350", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/aw2350", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bb7/b5c3/504124_mini.png?m=1611716806", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bb7/b5c3/504124_normal.png?m=1611716806", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bb7/b5c3/504124_large.png?m=1611716806", "created": 1597629937, "last_modified": 1611716806}, "last_reply_by": "xrzxrzxrz", "last_touched": 1710395608, "title": "周末去深圳，求推荐早茶和糖水铺子", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1023277", "created": 1710316620, "deleted": 0, "content": "周末去深圳，求推荐早茶和糖水铺子，北方人第一次去广东", "content_rendered": "<p>周末去深圳，求推荐早茶和糖水铺子，北方人第一次去广东</p>\n", "last_modified": 1710329799, "replies": 65, "id": 1023277}]